cb.xmi

Class XMIGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • cb.petal.DescendingVisitor
      • cb.xmi.XMIGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Visitor

    public class XMIGenerator
extends DescendingVisitor
    Convert a Rose petal file into the XMI format using NovoSoft's NSUML package which implements the entities defined in the UML specification 1.3.
    Version:
    $Id: XMIGenerator.java,v 1.8 2005/05/09 20:34:55 moroff Exp $
    Author:
    M. Dahm
